фик отчетности, чтобы уход был прозрачным."}]'::jsonb, '[{"title":"NINDS: Parkinson''s Disease","url":"https://www.ninds.nih.gov/health-information/disorders/parkinsons-disease"},{"title":"NINDS: Parkinson’s Disease - Hope Through Research","url":"https://www.ninds.nih.gov/sites/default/files/2025-05/parkinsons-disease-hope-through-research.pdf"}]'::jsonb, now()
);


