ила связи и график отчетности, чтобы уход был прозрачным."}]'::jsonb, '[{"title":"NHS: Find stoma support","url":"https://www.nhs.uk/service-search/other-health-services/stoma-support"},{"title":"Imperial NHS: Stoma care service","url":"https://www.imperial.nhs.uk/our-services/surgery/stoma-care"}]'::jsonb, now()
